    "body" : "<p>It seeems that the <code>java</code> binary does not have execution permission.  Executing <code>chmod a+x /usr/bin/java/jre-8u171-i586/bin/java</code> might solve the issue.</p>\n<p>But there is something wrong with how you installed java. I would try to install it using the <a href=\"http://doc.slitaz.org/en:handbook:packages\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">package manager</a>.</p>\n"
